## Add a text input to question 2

1. Go to the [textarea page of the Design System](https://design-system.service.gov.uk/components/textarea/).
2. Click **HTML** and copy the example HTML code.
3. Open `juggling-tricks.html` in your `app/views` folder
4. Replace the 2 example `<p>...</p>` paragraphs with the example HTML code you copied.
5. Delete the `label` and `span` sections. (Do not delete these in a real service.)
6. Replace `name="more-detail"` with `name="name-of-trick"`.

